metadata.name: NUDExGM
metadata.description:
In the gentle caress of morning's light,
A nude body bathed, untouched by night.
Awakening hues embrace the curves,
As dawn's embrace, a masterpiece it serves.

Soft tendrils of sunlight dance and play,
Upon skin bare, a sensual display.
Each ray, a painter's brush in the air,
Creating art upon a body so fair.

Silent whispers of the morning breeze,
A tender touch that brings a pleasing ease.
The body, a sculpture, so pure and free,
Bathed in light's embrace for all to see.
